data.description: Welcome Home! Beautifully updated 4 Bedroom Home on sizable lot W/ Detached Garage.  Office can be converted into a 5th bedroom!   Large Drive Way and Patio. Wonderfully maintained w/ updated Kitchen including Ceramic/Porcelain Tile Flooring throughout. Beautiful quartz countertops. Newer Roof! Newer HVAC and Recently serviced!  Backyard Oasis that is great for entertaining. Plenty of Storage. 3 Attic Accesses. Covered Storage Behind Garage. Located in one of the most established and desirable neighborhoods in Virginia Beach! Convenient access to Bases, Beaches, Shopping, Parks, Municipal Centers, Princess Anne Hospital and the Amphitheater/Sportsplex. Do not miss This incredible opportunity!  Fantastic Home. Move in Ready!
